          Built a VS Code plugin that simplifies i18n management across
          projects.
        </p></Experience
      >

      <Experience
        title="Frontend developer"
        where={{
          name: "Freelance",
        }}
        when={[new Date("2021-10-01"), new Date("2022-10-01")]}
        techno={["HTML5", "CSS3", "nodejs", "React"]}
